    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. It starts reliably, handles smoothly, and all major mechanical components are in solid working order. While the exterior and interior are very clean, you may find minor cosmetic imperfections consistent with regular use, such as small stone chips or light interior wear. It is a dependable choice for anyone looking for a quality vehicle that has many miles left to offer.",
