    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to the most exacting standards of automotive preservation. This vehicle retains a concours-level exterior finish and a pristine, factory-fresh interior environment. Every mechanical system has undergone a rigorous certification process to ensure peak operational integrity. This is an investment-grade opportunity for the discerning enthusiast who demands uncompromising quality and aesthetic perfection.",
